---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Autonomous Boat Propeller Optimization"
  description="Designed, simulated, and tested propeller geometries to improve autonomous boat performance."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Projects</p>

    <h1>Autonomous Boat Propeller Optimization</h1>

    <p class="intro">
      Designed, simulated, and tested multiple propeller geometries to improve
      the performance of an autonomous boat platform.
    </p>

    <img
      src="/images/projects/boat-propeller.jpg"
      alt="Autonomous Boat Propeller Optimization"
    />
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>

    <p>
      The objective of this project was to optimize propeller performance for
      an autonomous boat by balancing thrust, efficiency, and manufacturability.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Process</h2>

    <p>
      Multiple propeller geometries were designed in SOLIDWORKS and evaluated
      using flow simulation tools. Iterative improvements were made based on
      simulation results before prototypes were manufactured using 3D printing.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Tools Used</h2>

    <p>SOLIDWORKS • CFD • 3D Printing • Testing</p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 24px;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  section + section {
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .hero {
    max-width: 48rem;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }
</style>